text: Viorel Bubău (born 3 May 1961) is a Romanian equestrian. He competed in the individual eventing at the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Romania Category:Equestrians at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
